data-id=\"88402\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;line-height: 27.2px;widows: 1;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88402\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 27.2px;visibility: visible;\">\n     <section data-style=\"line-height: 1.8; text-align: justify; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(117, 114, 114);white-space: normal;\" style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n      <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n       <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n        <hr style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;visibility: visible;\">\n        <p style=\"margin: -1.2em 8px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\"></p>\n        <p style=\"margin: -1.2em 8px 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;clear: both;min-height: 1em;font-size: 17px;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75em;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-family: inherit;font-size: 1em;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:inherit;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 1em;font-family: inherit;text-decoration: inherit;visibility: visible;\"><span style=\"padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:inherit;text-decoration:inherit;font-size:18px;line-height:1.4;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;background-color:rgb(127, 127, 127);outline:0px;max-width:100%;font-family:inherit;\">新智元报道&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></strong></span></p>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section></h3>\n  <section style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px 8px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 1px;visibility: visible;\">编辑：KingHZ</span>\n  </section>\n  <section powered-by=\"xiumi.us\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:justify;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.544px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n    <section style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">\n     <h5 style=\"padding:10px;margin:10px 8px 0px;visibility:visible;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-size:14px;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;border-radius:3px;outline:0px;word-spacing:1px !important;max-width:100%;word-break:break-all !important;font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;visibility: visible;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;visibility: visible;\">【新智元导读】</strong>开源微调神器Unsloth带着黑科技又来了：短短两周后，再次优化DeepSeek-R1同款GRPO训练算法，上下文变长10倍，而显存只需原来的1/10！</span></h5>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">开源微调神器Unsloth带着黑科技又来了：<a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI3MTA0MTk1MA==&amp;mid=2652563935&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=cdc1aebe192494751960e3c00c7773a9&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"上次更新把GRPO需要的内存见到了8GB\" linktype=\"text\" imgurl=\"\" imgdata=\"null\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" tab=\"innerlink\" data-linktype=\"2\">上次更新把GRPO需要的内存见到了7GB</a>，这次</span><span style=\"font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">只需要5GB的VRAM，就能训练自己的推理模型Qwen2.5（1.5B），比上次要少2GB。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这次彻底把推理模型训练显存打下来了！</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这次把GRPO训练推理模型的上下文变长10倍，同时需要的显存少了90%。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">使用最新的Unsloth，只要5GB显存就能训练自己的推理模型，而且Qwen2.5-1.5B不会<span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">损失</span>准确率。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"395\" data-backw=\"551\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb2r3LA9an5WFDJKyNpCsvB6JOdDHfpT3Ea2NJ79rukYsmiaL2xC2tmzZpTN7NWqjiaDI4Jr9bqu7cbw/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx1=\"21.13879003558719\" data-cropx2=\"1080\" data-cropy1=\"0\" data-cropy2=\"760.9964412811387\" data-height=\"852\" data-imgfileid=\"505085896\" data-ratio=\"0.7176581680830972\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6e0819bd-1911-4525-a7ac-6e469b0abb00/public\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1059\" data-width=\"1208\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6e0819bd-1911-4525-a7ac-6e469b0abb00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">5GB显存什么概念呢？</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">16年开始发售的GPU比如GTX 1060的显存都有8GB。</span></span><span style=\"font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">16年<span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">GTX 1060放到现在，堪称电子古董！</span></span></span><span style=\"font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">目前，实现更长的上下文是GRPO面临的最大挑战之一。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">与其他GRPO LoRA/QLoRA实现相比，即使是基于Flash Attention 2（FA2）的实现，Unsloth新推出的高效GRPO算法上下文长度增加了10倍，同时使用的VRAM只要10%。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在配备TRL+FA2的GRPO设置中，Llama 3.1（8B）在20K上下文长度下，训练需要510.8GB的VRAM。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而Unsloth将VRAM减少了90%，降至仅54.3GB。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\">减少长上下文90%VRAM</p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">和使用Flash Attention 2的标准实现相比，Unsloth使用多种技巧，巧妙地把GRPO的VRAM使用量减少了90%多！</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在20K的上下文长度下，每个提示生成8次，Unsloth在Llama-3.1-8B模型上仅使用54.3GB的VRAM，而标准实现需要510.8GB（Unsloth减少了90%）。这一切得益于下列3项突破：</span>\n  </section>\n  <ol class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n    <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\">全新设计的内存高效线性算法：将GRPO的内存使用量削减了8倍以上，节省了68.5GB的内存。借助torch.compile，在num_generations=8和20K上下文长度下，实际上还更快。</span>\n    </section></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n    <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\">利用了Unsloth已发布的智能梯度checkpoint算法：将中间激活值异步卸载到系统RAM中，速度仅慢了1%。由于需要num_generations=8，这节省了高达372GB的VRAM。通过中间梯度累积，甚至可以进一步减少内存使用。</span>\n    </section></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;\">\n    <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 15px;\">与底层推理引擎（vLLM）共享相同的GPU/CUDA内存空间，不像其他包中的实现那样。这又节省了16GB的VRAM。</span>\n    </section></li>\n  </ol>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"185\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"518\" data-imgfileid=\"505085897\" data-ratio=\"0.3296296296296296\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b024ffd6-abd5-4551-1acb-8f5b5abada00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1570\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/b024ffd6-abd5-4551-1acb-8f5b5abada00/public\"></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Unsloth和基于Flash Attention 2（FA2）的标准实现内存比较</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在典型的GRPO标准实现中，需要创建两个大小为(8，20K)的logits来计算GRPO损失。这需要2*2字节*8（生成次数）*20K（上下文长度）*128256（词汇表大小）=78.3GB的VRAM。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Unsloth将长上下文GRPO的内存使用量削减了8倍，因此对于20K的上下文长度，只需要额外的9.8GBVRAM！</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">还需要以16位格式存储KV缓存。Llama3.18B有32层，K和V的大小均为1024。因此，对于20K的上下文长度，内存使用量=2*2字节*32层*20K上下文长度*1024=每个批次2.5GB。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">可以将vLLM的批次大小设置为8，但为了节省VRAM，在计算中将其保持为1。否则，需要20GB来存储KV缓存。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\">数学原理</p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">分组相对策略优化（Group Relative Policy Optimization，GRPO），出自DeepSeek去年发表的论文。</span></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如果一生只能读一篇DeepSeek的论文，网友建议选择首次提出GRPO的DeepSeekMath论文。</span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"156\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"284\" data-imgfileid=\"505085895\" data-ratio=\"0.27788649706457924\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4fa2cf7d-dc8d-40e1-eee0-c41152b5f800/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1022\" data-width=\"1022\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4fa2cf7d-dc8d-40e1-eee0-c41152b5f800/public\"></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 14px;\">论文链接：https://arxiv.org/abs/2402.03300</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">随后在DeepSeek的论文中，利用GRPO算法创建了DeepSeek-R1。</span>\n  </section>\n  <h2 style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">发现的问题</span></strong></span></h2>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在这里利用了Hugging Face的TRL GRPO实现。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">注意到，TRL实现的公式如下：</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"130\" data-imgfileid=\"505085893\" data-ratio=\"0.23636363636363636\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5d1cdb7c-48fd-4d03-babd-98ddc13b5900/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"550\" data-width=\"550\" style=\"width: 299px;height: 71px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5d1cdb7c-48fd-4d03-babd-98ddc13b5900/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">其中使用的是反向KL散度（而不是正向KL散度）。β是一个设为0.04的缩放因子，A是考虑所有奖励函数后得到的优势值。q是新训练的模型，P是原始参考模型。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">然后注意到，该实现将反向KL散度计算为：</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"536\" data-imgfileid=\"505085899\" data-ratio=\"0.4388888888888889\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4a800c9c-bfda-4d0a-42da-7ea33d263100/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1222\" style=\"width: 372px;height: 163px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/4a800c9c-bfda-4d0a-42da-7ea33d263100/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但这真的是正确的吗？</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">首先尝试推导并整理类似项：</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"772\" data-imgfileid=\"505085898\" data-ratio=\"0.8212765957446808\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/05f4c7dc-e00f-4a54-a321-4b66f004f700/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"940\" data-width=\"940\" style=\"width: 312px;height: 256px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/05f4c7dc-e00f-4a54-a321-4b66f004f700/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这意味着什么？实现中可能缺少一个与q（新分布项）的乘法吗？</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但这似乎是正确的，和DeepSeek-Math论文第14页首次引入GRPO时一样。</span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"187\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"506\" data-imgfileid=\"505085901\" data-ratio=\"0.3333333333333333\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/cc4a58a5-3c54-400c-d4f3-fb1cb7420800/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1516\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/cc4a58a5-3c54-400c-d4f3-fb1cb7420800/public\"></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">DeepSeek-Math论文第14页：在损失函数中添加KL散度，正则化GRPO算法</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">同样，John Schulman的博客也提到，反向KL项的无偏估计，实际上并不需要额外的q项。</span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"177\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"602\" data-imgfileid=\"505085902\" data-ratio=\"0.31574074074074077\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/30783a89-7280-4648-786f-a02be946ba00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1904\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/30783a89-7280-4648-786f-a02be946ba00/public\"></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">链接地址：http://joschu.net/blog/kl-approx.html</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在博客中看到：</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-height=\"322\" data-imgfileid=\"505085900\" data-ratio=\"0.5812274368231047\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8527df34-6e48-4092-3dea-da313aaa2400/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"554\" data-width=\"554\" style=\"width: 269px;height: 156px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8527df34-6e48-4092-3dea-da313aaa2400/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">还发现了一个有趣的现象：</span>\n  </section>\n  <section class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\">\n   <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\">\n    <li></li>\n   </ul>\n   <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"css\"><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">torch</span><span class=\"code-snippet__selector-class\">.exp</span>(<span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">q-q</span><span class=\"code-snippet__selector-class\">.detach</span>())&nbsp;*&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__selector-tag\">advantages</span><span class=\"code-snippet__selector-class\">.unsqueeze</span>(1)</span></code></pre>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这应该等于1，对吗？</span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"163\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"478\" data-imgfileid=\"505085909\" data-ratio=\"0.29074074074074074\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9e0cf9fc-8634-4b19-8098-7a775adc9500/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"1644\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/9e0cf9fc-8634-4b19-8098-7a775adc9500/public\"></p>\n  <section style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Hugging Face的TRL GRPO实现</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">实际上，发现这是必要的——似乎自动梯度autograd引擎可能无法正确传播梯度。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">因此，进行了4个实验：</span>\n  </section>\n  <ol start=\"1\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">使用参考实现的常规GRPO（红线）</span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">移除detach代码（蓝线）</span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: justify;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">按照之前讨论的完整反向KL，添加额外项（黄线）</span></p></li>\n   <li style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">\n    <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n     <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">使用正向KL散度代替（绿线）</span>\n    </section></li>\n  </ol>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"274\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"346\" data-imgfileid=\"505085903\" data-ratio=\"0.48732394366197185\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6d86387e-c8b1-4ca3-815e-b96dcdb56300/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"710\" data-width=\"710\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6d86387e-c8b1-4ca3-815e-b96dcdb56300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">总体来说，移除detach显然会破坏训练，所以必须保留它——这很可能需要进一步调查。其他实现似乎也类似？可能需要运行模型更长时间，以观察不同的效果。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在所有实现中，还利用了logsumexp技巧：</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"130\" data-backw=\"562\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_png/UicQ7HgWiaUb2r3LA9an5WFDJKyNpCsvB6kcsgfgnZZmB9iaXo3sy4j5SxDPJGGN6dTceYder3re0EhQ9VWFkLHiaQ/640?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx1=\"0\" data-cropx2=\"950\" data-cropy1=\"0\" data-cropy2=\"206.22775800711742\" data-height=\"220\" data-imgfileid=\"505085904\" data-ratio=\"0.2168421052631579\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1ff98858-16dd-438e-23a9-090150e8b700/public\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"950\" data-width=\"950\" style=\"width: 459px;height: 100px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/1ff98858-16dd-438e-23a9-090150e8b700/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\">Unsloth高效GRPO算法</p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <h1 style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\">但没想到华人工程师Horace He的线性交叉熵实现，带给unsloth灵感并成功应用于GRPO！</span></h1>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"320\" data-backw=\"320\" data-height=\"460\" data-imgfileid=\"505085907\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8a6cba59-7010-4eff-6470-e9cc69f14600/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"460\" data-width=\"460\" style=\"width: 57%;flex-basis: auto;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/8a6cba59-7010-4eff-6470-e9cc69f14600/public\"></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">Horace He，在Meta从事PyTorch相关工作</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">实际上，unsloth发现了一些令人惊讶的要点：</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">1 GRPO参考实现使用的是反向KL散度，而不是正向KL散度。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">2 如果不正确处理，在float16混合精度（以及float8）上直接实现线性交叉熵，并使用自动混合精度缩放机制，会导致崩溃。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">3 发现了GRPO损失实现中的其他一些奇怪之处，主要是在反向KL散度的公式表述方面。</span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"207\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"390\" data-imgfileid=\"505085906\" data-ratio=\"0.3686200378071834\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2cc3fe29-c88a-486e-d8ad-e3eb4ed5b000/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1058\" data-width=\"1058\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/2cc3fe29-c88a-486e-d8ad-e3eb4ed5b000/public\"></p>\n  <section style=\"text-align: left;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">线性交叉商链接：https://gist.github.com/Chillee/22cd93e11b887db1f596ab754d60a899</span>\n  </section>\n  <section autoid=\"1895\" data-style-type=\"0\" style=\"max-width:100%;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-bottom:0px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\">\n   <section style=\"padding: 8px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;border-left: 6px solid rgb(255, 202, 0);font-size: 18px;line-height: 1.4;font-family: inherit;font-weight: bold;text-decoration: inherit;border-top-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-right-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);border-bottom-color: rgb(255, 202, 0);overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">\n    <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\">其他功能</p>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">之前，unsloth只显示总聚合奖励函数本身，新版本为所有奖励函数提供完整的日志记录详情！</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-backh=\"213\" data-backw=\"562\" data-height=\"1023\" data-imgfileid=\"505085908\" data-ratio=\"0.3787037037037037\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/42a3186a-a729-4530-e5b2-6e2f6575cc00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-width=\"2701\" style=\"width: 100%;height: auto;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/42a3186a-a729-4530-e5b2-6e2f6575cc00/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">也不再需要调用函数来给GRPO打补丁了！也就是说，新版本会自动处理，可以删除下列代码：</span>\n  </section>\n  <pre style=\"text-align: justify;\"><section class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"><ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\"><li></li><li></li></ul><pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"javascript\"><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">from</span> unsloth <span class=\"code-snippet__keyword\">import</span> PatchFastRL</span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">PatchFastRL(<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"GRPO\"</span>, FastLanguageModel)</span></code></pre></section></pre>\n  <h1 style=\"text-align: center;margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\"><strong><span style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;font-size: 16px;\">vLLM推理选项</span></strong></span></h1>\n  <section style=\"text-align: justify;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;line-height: 1.75em;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">现在在vLLM中还能使用FP8 KV缓存，这可以在较新的GPU（RTX 3090、A100及更新型号）上将KV缓存空间使用量减少2倍。</span>\n  </section>\n  <pre style=\"text-align: justify;\"><section class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"><ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\"><li></li><li></li><li></li><li></li><li></li><li></li><li></li><li></li><li></li></ul><pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"properties\"><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__meta\">model,</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__string\">tokenizer = FastLanguageModel.from_pretrained(</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    <span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">model_name</span> = <span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"meta-llama/meta-Llama-3.1-8B-Instruct\",</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    <span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">max_seq_length</span> = <span class=\"code-snippet__string\">max_seq_length,</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    <span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">load_in_4bit</span> = <span class=\"code-snippet__string\">True, </span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    <span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">fast_inference</span> = <span class=\"code-snippet__string\">True, </span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    <span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">max_lora_rank</span> = <span class=\"code-snippet__string\">lora_rank,</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    <span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">gpu_memory_utilization</span> = <span class=\"code-snippet__string\">0.6, </span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    <span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">float8_kv_cache</span> = <span class=\"code-snippet__string\">True, </span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">)</span></span></code></pre></section></pre>\n  <p style=\"text-align: justify;margin: 24px 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">如果想在vLLM中使用min_p=0.1或其他采样参数，也支持传递vLLM的SamplingParams参数中的任何内容！</span></p>\n  <section class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\">\n   <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\">\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n    <li></li>\n   </ul>\n   <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"properties\"><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">max_prompt_length</span> = <span class=\"code-snippet__string\">256</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">from</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__string\">trl import GRPOConfig, GRPOTrainer</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">from</span> <span class=\"code-snippet__string\">unsloth import vLLMSamplingParams</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">vllm_sampling_params</span> = <span class=\"code-snippet__string\">vLLMSamplingParams(</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    <span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">min_p</span> = <span class=\"code-snippet__string\">0.1,</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    <span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">seed</span> = <span class=\"code-snippet__string\">3407,</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    <span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">...</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">)</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">training_args</span> = <span class=\"code-snippet__string\">GRPOConfig(</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    <span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">...</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    <span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">vllm_sampling_params</span> = <span class=\"code-snippet__string\">vllm_sampling_params,</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\">    <span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">temperature</span> = <span class=\"code-snippet__string\">1.5,</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><span class=\"code-snippet__attr\">)</span></span></code><code><span class=\"code-snippet_outer\"><br></span></code></pre>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\">参考资料：</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"white-space:normal;letter-spacing:0.544px;min-height:1em;line-height:1.75em;box-sizing:border-box !important;margin-right:8px;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;margin-left:8px;max-width:100%;font-family:-apple-system-font, system-ui, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-bottom:0px;text-align:left;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1px;\">https://unsloth.ai/blog/grpo</span></section>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "Unsloth 优化 GRPO 算法，大幅降低显存需求并扩展上下文，使“古董” GPU 也能高效训练大型模型。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "Unsloth 优化 GRPO 算法，大幅降低显存需求并扩展上下文，使“古董” GPU 也能高效训练大型模型。",
  "summary": "文章介绍了 Unsloth 对 DeepSeek 的 GRPO (Group Relative Policy Optimization) 训练算法的优化。通过内存高效线性算法、智能梯度 checkpoint 算法以及与底层推理引擎共享内存空间等技术创新，Unsloth 成功将训练推理模型所需的显存大幅降低，并显著增加了上下文长度。具体而言，Unsloth 将 VRAM 使用量减少了 90%，这意味着即使是较旧的 GPU，如 2016 年发布的 GTX 1060，也能用于训练复杂的推理模型，如 Qwen2.5-1.5B。此外，Unsloth 还发现并验证了 GRPO 参考实现中反向 KL 散度计算的潜在问题，并提供了更完整的日志记录和 vLLM 推理选项，进一步提升了 GRPO 算法的实用性和易用性。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Unsloth 大幅降低 GRPO 训练显存需求",
      "explanation": "通过内存高效算法、梯度 checkpoint 和内存共享，VRAM 使用量减少 90%，降低了 AI 模型训练的硬件门槛。"
